[CENTER][B][SIZE="6"][URL="https://sourceforge.net/projects/coltos/files/"][COLOR="SeaGreen"]Colt Enigma Download Link[/COLOR][/URL][/B][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[IMG]https://s26.postimg.cc/g3ehenhyh/Flashing_Instructions2.png[/IMG]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Verify that you're using the latest version of TWRP [/B][/SIZE]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Perform a FULL WIPE as described below if coming from another ROM or a different version of Android[/B]
   (A full wipe is when you wipe System + Data + Cache + Dalvik ART Cache)[/SIZE]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Flash the latest version of the ROM[/B][/SIZE]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Flash recommended GAPPS linked below[/B][/SIZE]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Flash Magisk if you want root[/B][/SIZE]

- [B][SIZE="3"]Reboot and ENJOY!![/B][/SIZE]

**[B][COLOR="Red"][SIZE="3"]If you fail to follow these instructions, please don't bother reporting any bugs[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]**
**[B][COLOR="Red"][SIZE="3"]If you use Xposed, please don't bother reporting any bugs[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]**
**[B][COLOR="Red"][SIZE="3"]If you use another kernel, please don't bother reporting any bugs[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]**


